Solid performance from my all time favourite, 'Old School' band RUSH.
 
In their captivating 'R30 World Tour'Concert


The R30 2 DVD set features Rush's Frankfurt, Germany concert in September 2004 near the close of their 30th Anniversary World Tour. 
The performance was captured with 14 cameras in high definition and is presented in 16:9 widescreen format. Audio options include 
Dolby Digital 5.1 Surround Sound or PCM Stereo.
